#Readme to install German Parser
################################

#Pre-requisites:
##############
* sudo apt-get install subversion
* ace parser 0.31 version need to be installed in $HOME/
* erg-2018-x86-64-0.9.31.dat.bz2 download in $HOME/ace-0.9.31/
  cd $HOME/ace-0.9.31/
  bunzip2 erg-2018-x86-64-0.9.31.dat.bz2 

1. Download German Parser from following link
        cd $HOME
	svn co http://svn.emmtee.net/trunk/dfki/gg/

2. cd $HOME/gg 
   $HOME/ace-0.9.31/ace -g  ace/config.parse.tdl -G ggp.dat

   (Note: Grammar file for german is ggp.dat)


To generate German sentence:
###########################

	sh eng_to_ger_shell.sh demo
